@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "Face Detection Module" as FaceDetectionModule
participant "Gesture Recognition Module" as GestureRecognitionModule
participant "Hand Tracking Module" as HandTrackingModule
participant "Interaction Module" as InteractionModule
participant "Collaboration Module" as CollaborationModule
participant "Latency Optimization Module" as LatencyOptimizationModule
FaceDetectionModule ->> HandTrackingModule : Detect face and trigger hand tracking
HandTrackingModule ->> GestureRecognitionModule : Track hand and send gesture data
GestureRecognitionModule -> InteractionModule : Recognize gesture and trigger interaction
InteractionModule ->> CollaborationModule : Trigger collaboration and enable real-time interaction
CollaborationModule ->> LatencyOptimizationModule : Optimize latency for real-time collaboration
LatencyOptimizationModule -> InteractionModule : Reflect action on projected surface with low-latency
FaceDetectionModule ->> GestureRecognitionModule : Send face detection data for gesture recognition
@enduml